905
01:00:35,460 --> 01:00:37,260
that's not a Friday the 13th movie.

906
01:00:38,060 --> 01:00:41,160
You're following around behind Jason,

907
01:00:41,420 --> 01:00:42,880
who's not quite Jason,

908
01:00:44,380 --> 01:00:46,920
as he walks through the woods,

909
01:00:46,920 --> 01:00:52,180
