910
01:00:52,720 --> 01:00:55,740
A couple of the kills go beyond brutal

911
01:00:55,740 --> 01:00:58,920
into like, terrifying, disgusting territory,

912
01:00:59,720 --> 01:01:01,660
or terrifying, if you will.

913
01:01:02,520 --> 01:01:04,300
I also just learned that Jason Patrick

914
01:01:04,300 --> 01:01:06,120
was just cast in Terrifier 3.

915
01:01:06,220 --> 01:01:07,040
I was like, what?

916
01:01:08,160 --> 01:01:10,780
Well, dude, the second movie was huge.

917
01:01:10,880 --> 01:01:11,580
It was huge.

918
01:01:11,860 --> 01:01:14,120
Yeah, the third one's going to be pretty big.

919
01:01:14,120 --> 01:01:14,980
Anyway.

920
01:01:16,540 --> 01:01:20,720
Yeah, they give you tiny touches of plot,

921
01:01:20,880 --> 01:01:24,640
or you can read more into what's going on aside from that,

922
01:01:24,700 --> 01:01:28,320
but for the most part, it feels like a video game

923
01:01:28,320 --> 01:01:30,220
where you're following Jason around

