It just doesn't hit moment to moment.

1177
01:13:29,140 --> 01:13:31,980
You don't care what's happening, and that's a problem, obviously.

1178
01:13:34,780 --> 01:13:37,420
I think it's a nice effort.

1179
01:13:38,000 --> 01:13:38,220
Yes.

1180
01:13:38,360 --> 01:13:40,280
It's not as good as Halloween.

1181
01:13:41,040 --> 01:13:41,240
No.

1182
01:13:41,900 --> 01:13:43,980
I'd put it above a Hills Have Eyes.

1183
01:13:46,940 --> 01:13:53,960
And again, it feels like one of those earlier stripped down works

1184
01:13:53,960 --> 01:13:57,760
of some of our fine horror directors.

1185
01:13:58,660 --> 01:14:01,060
And I think those movies are flawed, and I think this one's flawed too,

1186
01:14:01,060 --> 01:14:02,960
but overall I think it is worth a watch.

1187
01:14:03,540 --> 01:14:03,960
Yeah, I agree.

1188
01:14:04,100 --> 01:14:04,800
It's interesting.

1189
01:14:05,880 --> 01:14:07,480
And that's what I would say.

1190
01:14:07,560 --> 01:14:08,940
My hog is up.

1191
01:14:09,060 --> 01:14:11,580
It's not soaring, but it's fine.

1192
01:14:13,360 --> 01:14:13,520
Yeah.

1193
01:14:13,520 --> 01:14:17,440
Yeah, it left too much up to me,

1194
01:14:17,560 --> 01:14:21,820
and I didn't care enough to fill in all the cracks that are there in the movie, frankly.

1195
01:14:22,360 --> 01:14:24,420
There's one super memorable kill.

1196
01:14:25,080 --> 01:14:28,840
I think when you look at the slasher genre,

1197
01:14:28,840 --> 01:14:34,040
one super memorable kill is often enough to make a movie stand the test of time.

1198
01:14:35,100 --> 01:14:37,100
And this movie has some stuff going for it.

1199
01:14:37,200 --> 01:14:40,320
There's stuff I haven't seen before, vibes I haven't felt before,

1200
01:14:40,560 --> 01:14:42,920
but I don't want to see the movie a second time.

1201
01:14:45,040 --> 01:14:47,940
We are going to be back with a review of Bratz,

1202
